  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1981-06-24", 
    "text": "Authorizes appointment of a Northern Mariana Islands citizen who is qualified and indicates an intent to become a U.S. citizen: (1) as an officer in the U.S. armed forces; (2) in the Senior Reserve Officers' Training Corps; and (3) in the Armed Forces Health Professions Scholarship program. Declares that this Act expires upon the establishment of the Commonwealth of the Northern Mariana Islands."
